      "time": 15.62,
      "time_str": "00:15.620",
      "text": "Viumbe vyote vya mungu wetu na mfalme wetu",
      "translation": "创造的一切的神和主啊"
    },
    {
      "time": 19.48,
      "time_str": "00:19.480",
      "text": "Pazeni sauti ili nasi mwimbe",
      "translation": "我们为此以歌代泣"
